            "questionText": "<p>A company's SysOps administrator is troubleshooting communication between the components of an application. The company configured VPC flow logs to be published to Amazon CloudWatch Logs. However, there are no logs in CloudWatch Logs.<br><br>What could be blocking the VPC flow logs from being published to CloudWatch Logs?</p>",
            "explanation": "<p>ğŸ“ <strong><u>TÃ³m táº¯t Ä‘á»:</u></strong></p>\n<ul>\n    <li>\n        <p>CÃ´ng ty cáº¥u hÃ¬nh <strong>VPC Flow Logs</strong> Ä‘á»ƒ gá»­i dá»¯ liá»‡u vá» <strong>CloudWatch Logs</strong></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>Váº¥n Ä‘á»: <strong>KhÃ´ng cÃ³ log nÃ o xuáº¥t hiá»‡n</strong> trong CloudWatch Logs</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>Cáº§n tÃ¬m nguyÃªn nhÃ¢n cháº·n viá»‡c xuáº¥t báº£n logs</p>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p><p>âœ… <strong><u>ÄÃ¡p Ã¡n Ä‘Ãºng:</u></strong></p>\n<p><strong>The IAM policy that is attached to the IAM role for the flow log is missing the logs CreateLogGroup permission</strong></p>\n\n<p>CÃ¢u nÃ y Ä‘Ãºng vÃ¬ IAM role cá»§a VPC Flow Logs cáº§n Ä‘á»§ quyá»n Ä‘á»ƒ ghi log vÃ o CloudWatch Logs. Náº¿u thiáº¿u quyá»n <strong>logs:CreateLogGroup</strong>, Flow Logs sáº½ khÃ´ng thá»ƒ táº¡o log group trong CloudWatch vÃ  do Ä‘Ã³ khÃ´ng cÃ³ log nÃ o xuáº¥t hiá»‡n.</p>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>\n        <p>Theo tÃ i liá»‡u AWS, IAM policy cho Flow Logs pháº£i cÃ³ tá»‘i thiá»ƒu 5 quyá»n: <strong>CreateLogGroup, CreateLogStream, PutLogEvents, DescribeLogGroups, DescribeLogStreams</strong></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>Náº¿u thiáº¿u quyá»n CreateLogGroup, Flow Logs khÃ´ng thá»ƒ táº¡o log group ban Ä‘áº§u, dáº«n Ä‘áº¿n viá»‡c khÃ´ng cÃ³ log nÃ o Ä‘Æ°á»£c ghi</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>ÄÃ¢y lÃ  lá»—i phá»• biáº¿n khi táº¡o IAM role thá»§ cÃ´ng mÃ  quÃªn cáº¥p Ä‘á»§ quyá»n cáº§n thiáº¿t</p>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p><p>âŒ <u><strong>CÃ¡c Ä‘Ã¡p Ã¡n sai:</strong></u></p>\n\n<p></p><p>âŒ <strong>The IAM policy that is attached to the IAM role for the flow log is missing the logs CreateExportTask permission</strong></p>\n<ul>\n    <li>\n        <p>Quyá»n <strong>CreateExportTask</strong> chá»‰ dÃ¹ng khi báº¡n muá»‘n xuáº¥t logs tá»« CloudWatch sang S3, khÃ´ng pháº£i Ä‘á»ƒ ghi log tá»« VPC Flow Logs vÃ o CloudWatch</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>ÄÃ¢y khÃ´ng pháº£i quyá»n báº¯t buá»™c Ä‘á»ƒ Flow Logs hoáº¡t Ä‘á»™ng bÃ¬nh thÆ°á»ng</p>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p><p>âŒ <strong>The VPC is configured for IPv6 addresses</strong></p>\n<ul>\n    <li>\n        <p>VPC Flow Logs há»— trá»£ cáº£ IPv4 vÃ  IPv6 - viá»‡c VPC dÃ¹ng IPv6 khÃ´ng áº£nh hÆ°á»Ÿng Ä‘áº¿n kháº£ nÄƒng ghi log</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>IPv6 hoÃ n toÃ n tÆ°Æ¡ng thÃ­ch vá»›i VPC Flow Logs gá»­i Ä‘áº¿n CloudWatch</p>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p><p>âŒ <strong>The VPC is peered with another VPC in the AWS account</strong></p>\n<ul>\n    <li>\n        <p>VPC Peering khÃ´ng áº£nh hÆ°á»Ÿng Ä‘áº¿n viá»‡c ghi Flow Logs - báº¡n váº«n cÃ³ thá»ƒ thu tháº­p logs tá»« VPC Ä‘Ã£ peered bÃ¬nh thÆ°á»ng</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>Peering chá»‰ liÃªn quan Ä‘áº¿n káº¿t ná»‘i máº¡ng giá»¯a cÃ¡c VPC, khÃ´ng liÃªn quan Ä‘áº¿n cÆ¡ cháº¿ logging</p>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p><p>ğŸ”‘<strong><u>Tips and tricks:</u></strong></p>\n<ul>\n    <li>\n        <p>\"<strong>No logs in CloudWatch</strong>\" â†’ Kiá»ƒm tra <strong>IAM permissions cá»§a Flow Logs role</strong></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>\"<strong>VPC Flow Logs + CloudWatch</strong>\" â†’ Cáº§n 5 quyá»n: <strong>CreateLogGroup, CreateLogStream, PutLogEvents, DescribeLogGroups, DescribeLogStreams</strong></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>\"<strong>Flow Logs khÃ´ng hoáº¡t Ä‘á»™ng</strong>\" â†’ Äáº§u tiÃªn kiá»ƒm tra <strong>IAM role permissions</strong>, sau Ä‘Ã³ má»›i kiá»ƒm tra cáº¥u hÃ¬nh khÃ¡c</p>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p><p>ğŸ“– <strong><u>Reference:</u></strong></p>\n<ul>\n    <li>\n        <p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/vpc/latest/userguide/flow-logs-iam-role.html\">IAM Role for Publishing Flow Logs to CloudWatch Logs</a></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/vpc/latest/userguide/flow-logs-cwl.html\">Publish Flow Logs to CloudWatch Logs</a></p>\n    </li>\n</ul>",
