            "explanation": "<p>ğŸ“ <strong><u>TÃ³m táº¯t Ä‘á»:</u></strong></p>\n<ul>\n    <li>\n        <p>CÃ´ng ty dÃ¹ng <strong>CloudFormation</strong> Ä‘á»ƒ triá»ƒn khai háº¡ táº§ng</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>Váº¥n Ä‘á»: Má»™t user vÃ´ tÃ¬nh <strong>sá»­a thuá»™c tÃ­nh database</strong> trong template CloudFormation â†’ cáº­p nháº­t stack â†’ gÃ¢y <strong>giÃ¡n Ä‘oáº¡n á»©ng dá»¥ng</strong></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>YÃªu cáº§u: Team DevOps váº«n cÃ³ thá»ƒ deploy háº¡ táº§ng nhÆ°ng pháº£i <strong>ngÄƒn cháº·n viá»‡c sá»­a Ä‘á»•i ngoÃ i Ã½ muá»‘n</strong> trÃªn cÃ¡c tÃ i nguyÃªn quan trá»ng</p>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p><p>âœ… <strong><u>ÄÃ¡p Ã¡n Ä‘Ãºng:</u></strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Launch the CloudFormation templates using a stack policy with an explicit allow for all resources and an explicit deny of the protected resources with an action of Update:*.</strong></p>\n\n<p>ÄÃ¢y lÃ  cÃ¡ch Ä‘Ãºng vÃ¬ <strong>Stack Policy</strong> (chÃ­nh sÃ¡ch stack) Ä‘Æ°á»£c thiáº¿t káº¿ chÃ­nh xÃ¡c cho má»¥c Ä‘Ã­ch nÃ y - báº£o vá»‡ cÃ¡c tÃ i nguyÃªn cá»¥ thá»ƒ khá»i bá»‹ cáº­p nháº­t ngoÃ i Ã½ muá»‘n trong quÃ¡ trÃ¬nh update stack CloudFormation.</p>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>\n        <p>Stack Policy lÃ  má»™t tÃ i liá»‡u JSON Ä‘Æ°á»£c gáº¯n trá»±c tiáº¿p vÃ o CloudFormation stack, quy Ä‘á»‹nh hÃ nh Ä‘á»™ng cáº­p nháº­t nÃ o Ä‘Æ°á»£c phÃ©p trÃªn tá»«ng tÃ i nguyÃªn cá»¥ thá»ƒ</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>Cáº¥u trÃºc \"Allow táº¥t cáº£ + Deny riÃªng tÃ i nguyÃªn cáº§n báº£o vá»‡\" lÃ  pattern chuáº©n: cho phÃ©p team DevOps tiáº¿p tá»¥c deploy bÃ¬nh thÆ°á»ng, nhÆ°ng database vÃ  cÃ¡c tÃ i nguyÃªn quan trá»ng sáº½ bá»‹ khÃ³a khÃ´ng cho Update</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>HÃ nh Ä‘á»™ng <strong>Update:*</strong> bao gá»“m táº¥t cáº£ cÃ¡c loáº¡i cáº­p nháº­t (Modify, Replace, Delete) - Ä‘áº£m báº£o báº£o vá»‡ toÃ n diá»‡n</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>Stack Policy Ã¡p dá»¥ng cho táº¥t cáº£ user cÃ³ quyá»n CloudFormation, khÃ´ng cáº§n phÃ¢n quyá»n riÃªng tá»«ng ngÆ°á»i</p>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p><p>âŒ <u><strong>CÃ¡c Ä‘Ã¡p Ã¡n sai:</strong></u></p>\n\n<p></p><p>âŒ <strong>Set up an AWS Config rule to alert based on changes to any CloudFormation stack. An AWS Lambda function can then describe the stack to determine if any protected resources were modified and cancel the operation.</strong></p>\n<ul>\n    <li>\n        <p>AWS Config chá»‰ <strong>phÃ¡t hiá»‡n vÃ  cáº£nh bÃ¡o sau khi thay Ä‘á»•i Ä‘Ã£ xáº£y ra</strong>, khÃ´ng thá»ƒ ngÄƒn cháº·n trÆ°á»›c khi cáº­p nháº­t</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>Lambda khÃ´ng cÃ³ kháº£ nÄƒng \"há»§y\" má»™t stack update Ä‘ang thá»±c hiá»‡n - khi Lambda cháº¡y thÃ¬ thay Ä‘á»•i Ä‘Ã£ Ä‘Æ°á»£c apply rá»“i</p>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p><p>âŒ <strong>Set up an Amazon EventBridge event with a rule to initiate based on any CloudFormation API call. An AWS Lambda function can then describe the stack to determine if any protected resources were modified and cancel the operation.</strong></p>\n<ul>\n    <li>\n        <p>Giá»‘ng AWS Config, EventBridge chá»‰ <strong>pháº£n á»©ng sau khi API call Ä‘Ã£ Ä‘Æ°á»£c thá»±c thi</strong>, khÃ´ng thá»ƒ cháº·n trÆ°á»›c</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>CloudFormation khÃ´ng cÃ³ cÆ¡ cháº¿ cho phÃ©p Lambda \"rollback\" má»™t update Ä‘ang diá»…n ra - cÃ¡ch nÃ y phá»©c táº¡p, khÃ´ng reliable vÃ  khÃ´ng pháº£i giáº£i phÃ¡p Ä‘Æ°á»£c thiáº¿t káº¿ sáºµn</p>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p><p>âŒ <strong>Attach an IAM policy to the DevOps team role that prevents a CloudFormation stack from updating, with a condition based on the specific Amazon Resource Names (ARNs) of the protected resources.</strong></p>\n<ul>\n    <li>\n        <p>IAM policy kiá»ƒm soÃ¡t quyá»n trÃªn <strong>toÃ n bá»™ stack</strong>, khÃ´ng thá»ƒ chi tiáº¿t Ä‘áº¿n tá»«ng tÃ i nguyÃªn bÃªn trong stack má»™t cÃ¡ch hiá»‡u quáº£</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>Náº¿u deny UpdateStack thÃ¬ team DevOps sáº½ khÃ´ng thá»ƒ deploy báº¥t ká»³ thay Ä‘á»•i nÃ o - vi pháº¡m yÃªu cáº§u \"váº«n cho phÃ©p deploy\"</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>IAM khÃ´ng hiá»ƒu logic \"cho phÃ©p update resource A nhÆ°ng khÃ´ng cho update resource B trong cÃ¹ng 1 stack\"</p>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p><p>ğŸ”‘<strong><u>Tips and tricks:</u></strong></p>\n<ul>\n    <li>\n        <p>\"<strong>Prevent updates to specific resources</strong>\" â†’ <strong>Stack Policy</strong></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>\"<strong>Still allow team to deploy</strong>\" + \"<strong>Protect specific resources</strong>\" â†’ <strong>Allow all + Deny protected vá»›i Update:*</strong></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p>\"<strong>AWS Config/EventBridge + Lambda cancel</strong>\" â†’ <strong>Sai vÃ¬ reactive (pháº£n á»©ng sau), khÃ´ng pháº£i preventive (ngÄƒn cháº·n trÆ°á»›c)</strong></p>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p><p>ğŸ“– <strong><u>Reference:</u></strong></p>\n<ul>\n    <li>\n        <p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSCloudFormation/latest/UserGuide/protect-stack-resources.html\">AWS CloudFormation - Prevent updates to stack resources</a></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/prescriptive-guidance/latest/least-privilege-cloudformation/cloudformation-stack-policies.html\">AWS Prescriptive Guidance - CloudFormation stack policies</a></p>\n    </li>\n</ul>",
