            "questionText": "<p>A company hosts a web application on an Amazon EC2 instance in a production VPC. Client connections to the application are failing. A SysOps administrator inspects the VPC flow logs and finds the following entry:<br></p><pre><code class=\"language-json\">2 111122223333  eni-&lt;#2#3#&gt;  192.0.2.15  203.0.113.56  40711  443  6 1  40  1418530010  1418530070  REJECT  OK</code></pre><p><br><br>What is a possible cause of these failed connections?</p>",
